Changelog:

# OVERVIEW
- Small patch to fix bugs and make minor adjustments.

# General changes:
- Vines now wave.
- Round sun now has antialiasing and is bigger.
- Small changes to ambient occlusion.
- Fullbright mode was reworked to work better during night.

# Bugfixes:
- Fixed "Reflection info" compilation failure on AMD hardware.
- Fixed "dither13" failure on AMD hardware.
- Fixed a bug that caused aurora borealis to be distorted at far world positions, e.g., 30K+.
- Fixed blown image on Vanilla color scheme when using simpler exposure.
- Fixed a bug that caused soul lights to be too strong in hands.
- Fixed weird look on trees when using fullbright mode.
- Fixed fog intensity adjust not working on Nether.

